@node "Introduction" "Introduction of BGCheck"


         This is a door for the great SigmaExpress!
         
         
         This door is posting all files WHILE
         uploading.. so there is no need to wait till 
         the end of the batchupload!

         Why did i do this ?
     
         I have been waiting so long for a door like 
         this one but nobody did it. So i thought
         it is time do add a background filechecking
         and posting door. 


@endnode



@node "Requirements" "Requirements"


         What you need is:
         -----------------

         - OS 2.0x+
         - Sigma Express   
         - fast CPU! 

@endnode

@node "install" "How to Install!"

         The first thing you have to do is to create
         a drawer called Bgcheck in you bbs: directory.

         Then just copy all files from the bgcheck directory
         from this archive to your bbs:bgcheck/ dir.
         Then copy all files from the system directory from 
         this archive to your bbs:system/ dir.

         Now you have to edit your bbs:bgcheck/bgfilehandler.config
         

		NOT READY YET!	


@endnode


